Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Generated by SubOCR,ichi校正
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lu La Lu La
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,钢琴在绽放着\N世间梦想的原野上奏着旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,相信那坏掉的时钟\N时间是站在谁那边呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为何在我的心中会如此地\N等待着某个温柔的人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,美好的未来请告诉我吧\N月夜，月夜沈眠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lu La Lu La
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,苏醒的少女亲吻了\N回忆的苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在苦闷地揭开的书页中\N响起属于两人的钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,想紧紧地拥抱\N所以心爱的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,别再哭了喔\N再见，悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,奇妙的门上写着的字是\N『听而不闻的蛋糕』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderland欢迎你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fairyland是爱情的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Love's all way!\N每天都是软绵绵的小麦的诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕给你!今晚要吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,茶给你!星座的茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,窗口有天使在合唱\N你会听而不闻吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那『喜欢你』『喜欢你』的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}{\an8}[期待]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，下个月\N终于要举办校外教学了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像很期待嘛～千代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呵…呵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上校外教学已经取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚是骗你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，因为一看到千代笑成这样\N不自觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，这里有校外教学的手册\N我来念一下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,(发型改变)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…校外教学并不是去玩\N要了解这也是教学的其中一环
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是这么写的\N但一样是出去玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是可不能小看玩这件事啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在陌生的地方有限的时间内\N要玩得尽兴可是很难的喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在这之中不知有多少人\N在校外教学结束后仍有遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,终于到了校外教学了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第一次参加校外教学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，对了\N千代小学没毕业就跳级了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，我告诉你\N校外教学的规矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,规矩?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,土产要买木刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,木刀?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,木刀要配新撰组的法被
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,法被?\N(一种日式短袖上衫)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,法被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,千代…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不快分好组不行啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老师说过一组六个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，我跟千代跟大阪还有～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,阿榊与神乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有一组只要五个人就好 可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂，开这种玩笑太过份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,千代，你要看旅游指南吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哇～啊～好期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会非常有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候 会变成如此悲惨的一趟旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是连作梦也想不到…\N…这样如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,别配上奇怪的旁白!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,教人心动紧张的一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,阿历啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,阿智…差不多该起床(冲绳)啰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好，大家都到了吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没来的人举手!我在说啥啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有，我没来!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你人不是就在这吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好!那我们就出发往冲绳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在回到家之前就是校外教学啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好快啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,机场的土产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,心已经飞了\N(哇，你已经在买啦!)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我有点紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，坐了这么多人\N搞不好飞不起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，真的打算飞啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,机长!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喔喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好惊人的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就可以飞了!!飞吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哇…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\an8}[坐立难安]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,冲绳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,冲绳啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,蔚蓝的天空!啊啊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,HAISA!!哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，这是冲绳话吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,HAISA!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是午安的意思吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候，在冲绳要说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这种时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,痛啊痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要说『AGA』吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，这就是守礼门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，大概，一定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，好厉害，2000圆钞耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喔～啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶，好像耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,水印里面也有守礼门耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，这里有狮子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,『这是狮子吗?』\N冲绳语怎么说?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…『SI～SA～YAIBI～MI』吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,SI～SA～YAIBI～MI?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，SI～SA～YAIBIN\N(这是狮子啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,高中生六张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好，大家走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,冲绳!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,冲绳!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,冲绳!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也有排着一列狮子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,SI～SA～YAIBI～N\NSI～SA～YAIBI～N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,SI～SA～YAIBI～MI?(这是狮子吗?)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…SI～SA～AIBIRAN\N(那个不是狮子啦)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,冲绳!冲绳!冲绳!冲绳!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,到旅馆了\N喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐耶! 呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,噢!自助餐!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,限制解除!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎能输给你!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这个也要吃!这个也要吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊上啊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，是烩炒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，来到冲绳\N就非得吃这个不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有苦瓜烩炒，车麸烩炒\N面条烩炒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…还有…还有\N还有…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,烩炒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\an8}[海的藻屑]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，昨天是首里城\N今天是万座毛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉基本行程\N已经跑得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,呀喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是悬崖呢…是悬崖呢…\N好可怕喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,千代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好高好高喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，阿智别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,千代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,千代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,唉～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是可怕呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大阪，已经没事了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,呃?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,来，大家注意\N接下来是潜水体验
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这个项目我也会\N跟你们这组一起活动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喔～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,潜水我是超第一次!\N超期待的啊!是吧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，虽然我是有潜过水了啦\N但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，来把这个小鬼\N扔进海里吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,(海参)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大海～大海大海大海～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哈～太好玩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,呀，超好玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这哪是能用『超』一个字\N就可以形容得了的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有够…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有够好玩的呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要买什么土产呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,金楚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,金楚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要买吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,金楚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,金楚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,金楚糕，金楚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,金楚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，这个小狮子好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!?那个不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,每个的表情都有些不同\N果然有手工制的感觉耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…不，还是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我买这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,SI～SA～YAIBI～N～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大阪!神乐!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈，千代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好香的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在干嘛啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,阿智
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?是点心吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,开口笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是点心吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，没买阿智你们的份…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,开口笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一个多少钱?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,100圆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,开口笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪卖…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,开口笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哎，你吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,开口笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,开口笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,开口笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是在说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\an8}[梦之岛]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,榊同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的离岛计画\N你打算去哪里呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我这组是要去宫古岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是…\N西表山猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,咦…啊，你要去西表岛吗?\N请加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,会加油的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那件T恤…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，我是在那边的店买的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不，是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我去换衣服!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喔，看到了看到了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们再来确认一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,从大原港慢慢走向\N野生生物保护中心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙再一起去浦内川坐游览船\N看马流特(圆水潭)瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,接着再去上原买土产后回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…总之要注意\N别错过回去的船就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哇～那个是…\N岛耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,西表!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要拍啰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,换你啰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,山猫\N(注意，西表山猫会突然跑出)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,山猫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有山猫会出现!\N请减速!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有耶!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喔，好厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们也得减速呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没这必要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要去看西表山猫吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不，那大概是不可能的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以那么的期待…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,况且，这次的对象是山猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是随便几下就能了事的…\N(阿榊怕自己被山猫咬)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有可爱的山猫商品\N那就好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～什么都看不到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不过若是阿榊把手伸过去的话\N搞不好山猫就会跳出来咬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,阿榊好像被蛇盯住的青蛙一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,唉，没办法，神乐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,呀喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那副不管怎么看\N就像老虎的脸!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,短短的腿和粗粗的尾巴!\N身上的毛色斑纹!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有尖端圆圆的耳朵!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,YAMAPIKARYA!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\an8}[住在山里的猫]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,YAMAPIKARYA?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,YAMAPIKARYA\N就是西表山猫的本地叫法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,YAMAPIKARYA!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，它在跟榊同学撒娇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摸耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好，阿榊上啊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:19:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,把它抱起来吧! 紧紧的抱啊\N抱啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱喔，还是小猫呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,YAMAMAYA…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,YAMAMAYA!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,YAMAMAYA也是山猫的意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,YAMAPIKARYA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,YAMAPIKARYA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子长大后也会变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然后变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒的骨骼标本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，蛇在游泳呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哪…哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,耶!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,万岁!万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要分手了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们…我还是不能带你回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我家不能养猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你又是特别天然纪念物\N(保育类动物)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以跟来!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,榊同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,机场礼品…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,姜黄茶、姜黄茶、姜黄茶\N姜黄茶、姜黄茶、姜黄茶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,姜黄茶、姜黄茶、姜黄茶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,冲绳好好玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,榊同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还想再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.20,0:22:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还会…再来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.39,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(下集预告)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来了，来了，悄悄地来了\N看～吧，马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…什么…什么东西来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那还用问吗\N考试啊，大学考试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,从哪里?从哪里来呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,今年夏天也要去\N千代家的别墅，G0!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这次是考前冲刺集训!!\N游泳啊!玩乐啊!劈西瓜啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,够啦，还不给我去念书!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,心有着翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,传达出心中的轻声细语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，乘风而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,心在星星彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,愿望必会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,来此相遇\N那是通往未来的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在窗边悄悄的喊叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.71,0:23:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是恋爱的预感\N而…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是还远在他方的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信着明天\N我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,覆盆子天堂，不再孤独\N是约定了的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,覆盆子天堂，甜蜜的泪\N在乐园中也展露微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,覆盆子天堂，迎面而来的\N是温柔梦境天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,覆盆子天堂\N我正在回到你怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当乐园的花绽放之日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.19,0:24:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你两人\N两人再相逢吧
